{"tid":1752370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"耍開橫手都輸嘅建制反映真實嘅民意比例","createTime":"2019-11-24T19:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T05:24:37.000Z","uid":167802,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"74f1693e874e18fe090d730e73c1a1b0a8ee5587","tid":1752370,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:58:12.000Z","msg":"2015年區議會選舉<br />\n非建制派得票率約40%<br />\n<br />\n到今日<br />\n2019年區議會選舉<br />\n非建制派得票率喺呢刻暫時係60%<br />\n<br />\n香港嘅主流民意自2014起(其實甚至更早)<br />\n就絕對係本土/泛民遙遙領先<br />\n只係大家都知道建制派耍開橫手<br />\n蛇齋餅粽、種票、掌心雷&hellip;咩都好<br />\n先得出2015年咁嘅結果<br />\n<br />\n因此<br />\n用嚟反映民意的話<br />\n目前泛民60%嘅得票率就絕不可能以帳面解讀<br />\n保守假設喺2015年本土/泛民嘅實際民意係60%<br />\n咁我哋今時今日嘅民意支持度就可以理解為<span style=\"color: red;\">80%以上</span><br />\n<br />\n因為實有人出嚟講「兩邊嘅支持度都唔係差好遠啫」之類嘅歪論<br />\n喺度打定個底先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有<br />\n我哋未贏<br />\n路還很遠<br />\n唔好鬆懈<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"78e62b4e84de750023dde415f080a7efef0338ce","tid":1752370,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:59:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"477d72c7b9b45de9bd94a9eca384f79b9eb4dea6","tid":1752370,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:00:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c459f12533603ffd6705f5a52ea1ef579b65782f","tid":1752370,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:00:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dec88b082694b4708d400b21df76aea1784540ad","tid":1752370,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:00:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14cb1061bd68fa827236846c6fc7e7fb28c65624","tid":1752370,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"