,"msg":"推"},{"pid":"764bcca06b697e6409a4668ba96823c4029ea165","tid":1752370,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:18:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47100f0e5b7769570832237aa0878505eb6d5fe2","tid":1752370,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:18:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4521587f02de8219659c00b7f30eba861ba680c3","tid":1752370,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:19:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07e484db82fe4fee4a7ee496fe0f8ce574d5649d","tid":1752370,"uid":114822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbead2f6bd10c0f60b5a752ab3c6e8a470a808e3","tid":1752370,"uid":167802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:56:34.000Z","msg":"頂<br />\n今日真係好多人討論話民意得6成，唔好鬆懈咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:20:10.000Z","msg":"呢個先係正確態度<br />\n親共派最另叻就係無恥 係人都知佢地種票 收買廢老 呃廢老投票etc 但偏偏有埋證據都無用 佢地照做 仲拎個結果黎再呃人<br />\n與其話我地有8成 不如諗下點樣制裁嘅選舉舞弊嘅親共狗"},{"pid":"9b15fadad41d9c0c4051cc0898e393a947c47587","tid":1752370,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbead2f6bd10c0f60b5a752ab3c6e8a470a808e3","tid":1752370,"uid":167802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:56:34.000Z","msg":"頂<br />\n今日真係好多人討論話民意得6成，唔好鬆懈咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:20:27.000Z","msg":"唔好鬆懈係正確..."},{"pid":"698dd1bd117b7998cdf2ffc521b90b3300d93f4f","tid":1752370,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:24:37.000Z","msg":"民意唔係贏咁解<br />\n但民意要成為我哋嘅戰略<br />\n我哋嘅武器<br />\n如是，就要對民意先有合適嘅理解<br />\n<br />\n和理非係時候繼續推/討論黃色經濟圈同埋聯合罷工戰線<br />\n好期望有區議會助攻"}]}